Privacy Policy for [KING THE RULER]

Effective Date: [12-07-2024]

This Privacy Policy explains how [KING THE RULER] ("we", "our", or "the bot") collects, uses, and protects information about users ("you" or "users") of our Discord bot. By using [Your Bot's Name], you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

1. Information We Collect
a. User Data
When you interact with [KING THE RULER], we may collect the following types of information:

User ID: Your unique Discord user ID.
Username and Discriminator: Your Discord username and discriminator (e.g., Username#1234).
Messages and Commands: The content of messages and commands you send to the bot.
b. Server Data
When the bot is added to a server, we may collect the following server-specific information:

Server ID: The unique identifier for the server.
Server Name: The name of the server.
Channel IDs: The unique identifiers for channels within the server.
2. How We Use Information
a. Providing Services
We use the collected information to provide and improve the functionality of [Your Bot's Name], including responding to commands, managing server settings, and executing tasks as requested by users.

b. Analytics
We may use anonymized and aggregated data to analyze usage patterns and improve the bot’s performance and features.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. However, we may share information in the following circumstances:

With Your Consent: We may share information with your consent or at your direction.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.
4. Data Security
We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

5. Data Retention
We retain collected data for as long as necessary to provide the bot's services or as required by applicable laws. If you would like your data to be deleted, please contact us and we will comply with your request in accordance with applicable laws.

6. Third-Party Services
[Your Bot's Name] may use third-party services that collect, monitor, and analyze data to enhance the bot’s functionality. These third-party service providers have their own privacy policies addressing how they use such information.

7. Children's Privacy
[Your Bot's Name] is not intended for use by anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the effective date. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

9. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

